  "abstract": "The 22 entry (1987) IPMSN was conducted at one location in India and two in West Africa. The across location mean smut severities for the test entries varied from 1-38% compared with 61% and 56% for the susceptible checks BJ 104 and ICMH 83202, respectively...",
